short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Keep track of time for your e-food orders and view interesting analytics.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension helps you track your e-food orders by automatically adding a countdown timer when a new order is placed. You can view the countdown, an estimated arrival time, and info about the store you ordered from, at any time by opening the extension's popup.
You can also view interesting analytics about your total orders, easily, with the click of a button!
